data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the highly sought-after city of Jonesville. With its appealing location, comfortable living spaces, and amenities, this property offers an ideal opportunity for a growing family or anyone seeking a cozy home in a desirable community. Fenced in back yard, main level laundry, 2-car detached garage. Short distance from downtown, where you can find a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options. The city also boasts excellent schools, beautiful parks, and easy access to major transportation routes, making it an ideal location for families and commuters alike. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming Jonesville home yours today. Call the listing agent to view this property.
